  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Just as certain serpents can spray poison from their fangs, as a swift action, you can spit a gout of life-stealing venom onto a weapon you are wielding. The poison lasts for 1 minute or until you make an attack with that weapon that injures a foe.&nbsp;Life-Stealing Venom: Injury;&nbsp;save&nbsp;Fort DC 10 + half your class level + your Wisdom modifier;&nbsp;frequency&nbsp;1/round for 3 rounds;&nbsp;effect&nbsp;1 Con damage;&nbsp;cure&nbsp;1 save. You can use the venomous saliva ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your Wisdom modifier.</p>\n<p>This power replaces the Venomous Stare power of the Scalykind Domain.</p>"
